  %h3 www.loomio.org (An instance of Loomio)

  %p
    www.loomio.org is an instance of Loomio operated by the Loomio Cooperative, running upon the Heroku platform.

  %h3 private managed Loomio hosts
  %p
    Loomio offers a private managed host service to customers. With this service Loomio will setup and manage a Loomio install on the customer's choice of domain name and hosting provider.

  %p Each instance of Loomio is separate. Signing up to one instance does not sign you up to another, following this rule, you will need to consent per Loomio instance that you wish to use and you will need to withdraw consent per instance that you no longer wish to have process your personal data.

