%section
  Key GDPR questions
  %h3 Upon what legal basis are you justifying holding this data? Consent or legal requirements?
  %p Our terms and conditions currently indicate that use of the service grants us the legal right to hold your data. We're going to upgrade this consent process to make it super explicit.

  %h3 Who has access to that data?
  Within Loomio.org, just the people responsible for keeping the services running have access to your data.

  %h3 How are you protecting that data from breaches?
  The security of the storage and processing of your data is trusted with the data processor.

  %h3 What else is that data being used for?

  %h2 Breach reporting
  We will report any breach of data within 72 hours. To where, and how?

